description.en:
Building the $Frens metaverse, inspired by Pepe the Meme.

First ever $FRENS token to create a Pub community for the NFT space. Free beers for everyone while building the metaverse of Pepe the Meme.

Created as a tribute to Pepe the Meme, the real Fren who decided to dedicate his life to becoming the #1 meme.
